  "prompt": "How much do I need to earn monthly to live in Shanghai, China?",
  "response": "Living costs in Shanghai can vary widely depending on your lifestyle, accommodation preferences, and spending habits. Here's a breakdown of average monthly expenses to help you estimate how much you might need to earn:\n\n### **1. Accommodation**\n- **Rent (1-bedroom apartment in city center):** \u00a58,000\u201315,000  \n- **Rent (1-bedroom apartment outside city center):** \u00a54,000\u20138,000  \n- **Shared accommodation:** \u00a52,500\u20135,000  \n\n### **2. Utilities (electricity, water, gas, internet)**\n- **Monthly:** \u00a5500\u20131,000  \n\n### **3. Food**\n- **Cooking at home:** \u00a51,500\u20133,000  \n- **Eating out (mid-range restaurants):** \u00a53,000\u20135,000  \n\n### **4. Transportation**\n- **Public transport (subway/bus):** \u00a5200\u2013500  \n- **Taxi/ride-hailing services:** \u00a5500\u20131,500  \n- **Car ownership (if applicable):** \u00a52,000\u20134,000 (insurance, gas, parking)  \n\n### **5. Entertainment and Leisure**\n- **Movies, cafes, bars:** \u00a51,000\u20133,000  \n- **Gym membership:** \u00a5300\u2013800  \n\n### **6. Shopping and Miscellaneous**\n- **Clothing, personal care, etc.:** \u00a51,000\u20133,000  \n\n### **7. Health Insurance**\n- **International health insurance:** \u00a51,000\u20133,000  \n- **Local health insurance:** \u00a5500\u20131,000  \n\n### **Total Estimated Monthly Living Costs:**\n- **Budget lifestyle:** \u00a58,000\u201312,000  \n- **Comfortable lifestyle:** \u00a512,000\u201320,000  \n- **Luxury lifestyle:** \u00a520,000\u201340,000+  \n\n### **Additional Considerations**\n- If you have dependents, schooling costs for children can add significantly to your expenses.  \n- Expatriates often earn higher salaries and may receive housing allowances or other benefits.  \n\nAs a general rule, earning **\u00a515,000\u201325,000 per month** can provide a comfortable lifestyle for a single person, while higher earnings may be necessary for families or luxury living.",
